cart.title: Women Cotton Denim Abaya
cart.description:
We are offering the latest and the best in women's clothing and accessories, for all occasions. Our Dark Blue Women Cotton Denim Abaya has a traditional,modest, plain, and full sleeve buttoned and is comfortable to wear and remove within no time. It is very easy to match your other wardrobe items with this beautiful abaya.
The gorgeous color will make you feel confident and beautiful on your special day. 
Handcrafted and beaded products should be washed inside out in a delicate program
During the wash in order not to spoil the product, do not exceed 30 °C 
 Wash the product by the washing instructions 
Use appropriate detergent for colored products 
Denim products and dark-colored products may dye when washed with other light-colored products. Do not wash together
Do not expose clothes to direct sunlight while drying
